 Lee Myung Bak of south Korea is busy kicking off war hysteria, trumpeting about joint military exercises with the U.S. This once again clearly indicates that the south Korean authorities are chiefly to blame for blocking the development of the inter-Korean relations, not standing for dialogue. &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
